article_title: White House says Obama would veto House bill to repeal Obamacare
article_text: WASHINGTON The White House issued a veto threat on Monday for a bill from the Republican-controlled U.S. House of Representatives bill that would repeal President Barack Obama's signature healthcare legislation, the Affordable Care Act, known as Obamacare.
